The paper proposes a strategy for optimal demand response of an HVAC system using supervised learning. This involves training artificial neural networks and using them to optimize scheduling for price-based demand response. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.LG (Machine Learning), followed by cs.SY (Systems and Control), cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence), cs.CE (Computational Engineering, Finance, and Science), and cs.SE (Software Engineering).
